text: Rich Zecher (born October 14, 1943) is a former American football defensive tackle. He played for the Oakland Raiders in 1965, the Miami Dolphins from 1966 to 1967 and for the Buffalo Bills in 1967. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:American football defensive tackles Category:Utah State Aggies football players Category:Oakland Raiders players Category:Miami Dolphins players Category:Buffalo Bills players
